8
00:00:24,720 --> 00:00:26,500
Kita sudah berjanji, 'kan?

9
00:00:29,380 --> 00:00:31,040
Akhirnya kupaham.

10
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:33,960
Aku telah kembali ... ke saat ini!

11
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:36,700
