13
00:00:42,570 --> 00:00:43,590
Halo?

14
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:45,570
Kau telah berhasil, ya.

15
00:00:45,810 --> 00:00:47,580
Hah?
Siapa?

16
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:50,820
