Setelah kuselidiki, ternyata insiden yang
menyebabkan kematian Kakakku pun tak terjadi.

39
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:05,350
Eh? Perseteruan Touman tak terjadi?

40
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:06,270
Benar.

41
00:02:06,910 --> 00:02:10,380
Tapi tak kusangka kau akan berhasil.

42
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,300
Hah?

43
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,920
Apa maksudnya, tuh?

44
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:15,820
Soalnya, kau itu sampah, 'kan?

45
00:02:16,010 --> 00:02:18,600
Dasar keparat.
'Ngajak gelut, nih?

46
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:22,200
Kalem saja, toh kita mau bertemu Kakakku.

47
00:02:22,329 --> 00:02:23,200
Ah.

48
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:26,170
