68
00:04:20,010 --> 00:04:24,380
Lalu di tengah malam bermandikan hujan

69
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:32,150
kita ikrarkan balas dendam!

70
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:40,880
(#12 Balas Dendam)

