107
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:07,800
Mana mungkin aku bisa menemuinya.

108
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:10,430
Meski berulang kali kulintasi waktu,

109
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:12,830
