148
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,600
Aku tak tahan sama situasi ini.

149
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,210
Kalian saja yang mengatasinya.

150
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:03,390
Selamat tinggal.

151
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:06,920
Kalau kami berduaan, jantungku
